                        <td class="border_bottom_0.75"></td>
                        <td colspan="2" class="border_bottom_0.75 cellpadding_bottom_5 cellpadding_top_5">Bail
                            refused. Remanded in jail custody because there are substantial grounds
                            for believing that the accused would—</td>
                        <td align="center" class="border_right_0.75 border_bottom_0.75 cellpadding_top_5">□</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="border_left_0.75"></td>
