                        <td class="border_right_0.75 valign_bottom" align="center">□</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="border_left_0.75"></td>
                        <td>(<i>f</i>)</td>
                        <td colspan="5" class="cellpadding_right_15 align_justified">Alleged to have
                            committed this/these offence(s) while on bail for other matters.</td>
                        <td class="border_right_0.75 valign_top" align="center">□</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="border_left_0.75"></td>
                        <td>(<i>g</i>)</td>
                        <td colspan="5" class="cellpadding_right_15 align_justified">Criminal record
